x
21\equiv 385\pmod x\quad \text{and}\quad 587\equiv 167\pmod x 
a\equiv b \pmod x
x
a - b
x\mid (a - b)
x\mid (385 - 21) = 364\quad\text{and}\quad x\mid (587 - 167) = 420
x = \gcd(364, 420) = \color{blue}{\bf 4\cdot 7} = 28
